PDFTools is a collection of minor-modes centered around a server
querying PDF documents for all kinds of informations.

The code is on github: http://github.com/politza/pdf-tools

It supports
* Isearching documents,
* browsing PDF Outlines via Imenu,
* following internal and external links,
* copying text with the mouse and
* some other stuff.

http://www.hochschule-trier.de/~politza/emacs/pdf-tools.png

This is not spam !
